reviews.name: ashmed rampersaud
reviews.title: Buy a better cpu cooler
reviews.review: This is a great processor, the only problem I have with it , is that it comes with a tiny cpu heat sink and fan and there is no pack of thermal paste for you to use on other cpu coolers . it is already on the heat sink . so you have to buy a pack of thermal paste if you are trying to upgrade the cpu cooler. Also the fins on the stock intel are thin. I paid 25-30 for the other one and it is thick in every way .
